# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

{{#each releases}}

  {{#if href}}
    ##{{#unless major}}#{{/unless}} [{{title}}]({{href}})
  {{else}}
    ##{{#unless major}}#{{/unless}} {{title}}
  {{/if}}
  {{#if tag}}
    > {{niceDate}}
  {{/if}}

  {{! TODO: Test the merge template }}
  {{#each merges}}
    - {{message}} {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/each}}

  {{! List commits with `Breaking change: ` somewhere in the message }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='#### :rotating_light:  Breaking Changes  :rotating_light:' message='breaking changes: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits that add new features, but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='#### :sparkles:  New Features' message='feat: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits with changes inside (Default), but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='#### :wrench:  Changed' exclude='breaking changes: |feat: |fix: |deprecated: |removed: |security: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits with deprecated changes, but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='####  :warning:  Deprecated' message='deprecated: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits that add fixes, but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='#### :bug:  Fixed' message='fix: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits with deprecated changes, but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='####  :no_entry_sign:  Removed' message='removed: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{! List commits with deprecated changes, but not those already listed above }}
  {{#commit-list commits heading='#### :lock:  Security' message='security: '}}
    - {{subject}} [`{{shorthash}}`]({{href}})
  {{/commit-list}}
{{/each}}